WEBVTT

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:04.221
when a civil war broke out in July 2016.

00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:05.999
It was a long weekend

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.635
and most people were on a holiday,

00:05:08.840 --> 00:05:11.095
just me and one more person
were on duty there.

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:14.479
There was firing all over,

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:18.719
bullets in our compound,
mortar shells strewed everywhere.

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:21.621
I took over the six-bed clinic

00:05:22.480 --> 00:05:26.785
and treated 60-70
patients every day.

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:33.182
They would come with a hand
or a leg missing,